snippet.title: Islanders: VR Edition - Official Release Date Reveal Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Islanders: VR Edition will be available on Meta Quest on September 28, 2023. Watch the latest trailer for another look at this relaxing minimalist strategy game about building cities on colorful islands.
